title: Warhammer Fantasy Army book Warriors of Chaos 8E  - 2012
description: From the magic-swept lands of the frozen north march the Warriors of Chaos, an indomitable race of battle-hungry killers and mutant monsters who fight for glory and the favour of bloodthirsty gods. Led to war by inhumanly powerful Champions, armed and armoured in Daemon-forged steel, and imbued with the raw power of Chaos itself, the worshippers of the Ruinous Powers never tire in their eternal quest to drown the world in a tide of death and destruction.
